defaultArticle 32 of the 
defaultConvention on the Rights of Pedefaultople with disabilities defaultcalls for 
defaultstates to ensure 
defaultthat international cooperation, including international development programmes, 
defaultare
default inclusive of and accessib
defaultle to persons with disabilities. This highlights the need for DFID to ensure a disability strategy is in place across their programmes. 
